---
title: Turkish Chickpea & Cauliflower Bowls with Cilantro Couscous & Creamy Feta Sauce
description: Roasted chickpeas are one of our chefs’ current obsessions—in the oven, they turn delightfully crunchy, making them a perfect topping for salads, grain bowls, and even on their own as a party appetizer. Here, we toss them with a Turkish spice blend for earthy, smoky flavor, then roast until crispy. They’re paired with cauliflower seasoned with more of the same spices and served over cilantro-flecked couscous with a drizzle of creamy feta sauce. Prepare to be totally bowled over.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/turkish-chickpea-cauliflower-bowls-fa51d8e3.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/turkish-chickpea-cauliflower-bowls-5f0493a0048af133df599c78-acf82d07.pdf
